                  <p>This Privacy Policy requires that your request satisfy applicable laws and regulations and the following conditions:<br>
                  (1)    Through CoolPad's exclusive access of request and for the protection of your information security, your request should be in writing (unless the local law explicitly recognizes the oral request);<br>
