                  <p>Depending on the extent of your withdrawal of consent, please note that you may not be able to continue receiving the full benefit of CoolPad’s products and services. The withdrawal of your consent or authorization will not affect the validity of our processing carried out on the basis of the consent up until the point of withdrawal.</p>
